Goals

- Terminal ASCII map 20x12, player @, obstacles #, empty .
- Movement validated by grid
- Minimal tags on Player, Monster, Ability
- Three abilities registered: bolt, push, focus (intent only)

Content

- Maps: name, width, height, blocked
- Monsters: id, name, tags, stats, abilities
- Spells: id, name, tags, cost_ap, range_min, range_max, effects

Constraints

- Pure engine logic; terminal-only UI
- JSON validated by pydantic
- No networking, no iso renderer, no inventory